---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import ContactCTA from "../components/ContactCTA.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import animation from "@/utils/animations";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Yannik Sahl" description="About Yannik Sahl">
  <div transition:animate={animation} class="stack gap-20">
    <main class="wrapper about">
      <Hero
        title="About"
        tagline="Thanks for stopping by! Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
      />
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="pb-2">
            Since I can remember I've found computers to be these fascinating,
            ✨magical✨ machines that could do <i>anything</i>. So I studied
            them and found out that they're actually not all that smart, but in
            the hands of the right people they could <i>feel</i> magic.
          </p>
          <p>
            So from then on I too would wanted to become a computer wizard which
            led me down the path of software development. Over the years of
            sometimes more and sometimes less wizardy things I've picked up
            quite a versatile set of skills and experiences that today help me
            fulfill that role the best I ever could. Read more about those below
            ⬇️
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p class="mb-8">
            I've studied for and completed two Bachelor programs in the
            following fields:
          </p>
          <div
            class="edu-card relative text-[#c3cadb] rounded-3xl p-6 mb-8 border-[1px] border-[var(--gray-800)] overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="image absolute top-0 left-0 rounded-3xl h-full w-full -z-10"
            >
              <img
                src="/assets/computer.webp"
                class="!m-0 object-cover object-center w-full h-full blur-sm"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between pb-4">
              <p>B.Sc. Computer Engineering</p>
              <p><i>2018 to 2020</i></p>
            </div>
            <ul class="pl-8 list-disc">
              <li class="pb-2">Studied for 4 semesters at HTW Berlin</li>
              <li class="pb-2">
                Specialization in advanced programming, embedded systems and IT
                security
              </li>
              <li>Graduated with a final grade of 1.5</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div
            class="edu-card relative text-[#c3cadb] rounded-3xl p-6 mb-8 border-[1px] border-[var(--gray-800)] overflow-hidden"
          >
            <div
              class="image absolute top-0 left-0 rounded-3xl h-full w-full -z-10"
            >
              <img
                src="/assets/business.webp"
                class="!m-0 object-cover object-bottom w-full h-full blur-sm"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between pb-4">
              <p>B.Sc. Business Administration</p>
              <p><i>2015 to 2018</i></p>
            </div>
            <ul class="pl-8 list-disc">
              <li class="pb-2">
                Studied for 5 semesters at FU Berlin and spent one semester
                abroad at UNAV in Pamplona, Spain
              </li>
              <li class="pb-2">
                Specialization in finance, management accounting and business
                informatics
              </li>
              <li>Graduated with a final grade of 2.0</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p>
            I'm also a qualified E.M.T. which is a skill I picked up in 2022 and
            briefly worked as in 2023.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>(Work in Progress)</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>(Work in Progress)</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <ContactCTA />
  </div>

  <style>
    .image:after {
      content: "\A";
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      transition: all 0.5s;
      -webkit-transition: all 0.5s;
    }
    .edu-card:hover .image:after {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .about {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }

    img {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-200);
    }

    .section-title {
      grid-column-start: 1;
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      color: var(--gray-0);
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }

    .content {
      grid-column: 2 / 4;
    }

    .content :global(a) {
      text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
      text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
      transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
    }

    .content :global(a:hover),
    .content :global(a:focus) {
      text-decoration-color: currentColor;
    }

    @media (min-width: 50em) {
      .about {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
      }

      .about > :global(:first-child) {
        grid-column-start: 2;
      }

      section {
        display: contents;
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
      }
    }
  </style>

